{"tid":2236002,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"台美盟軍嚴防走火 中共閃電登陸勢落空","createTime":"2020-10-09T06:50:34.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-09T13:37:52.000Z","uid":239336,"like":87,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":51,"replies":[{"pid":"f88adadef5a3a02e6dcd01d2e77ce694afcf37e1","tid":2236002,"uid":239336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-09T06:50:34.000Z","msg":"武統台灣一直是大陸的選項，明日是台灣雙十節，今年中共軍機擾台多達1,710次，闖入台海中線多達49架次，戰火味道近20年最濃烈，隨時擦槍走火。台灣前總統馬英九認為大陸一旦武統台灣，將是「首戰即終戰」，寶島瞬間潰敗。本報邀得台灣國防安全研究院國防資源與產業研究所長蘇紫雲、中正大學戰略暨國際事務研究所兼任助理教授林穎佑，以及澳門軍事評論員黃東作武統台灣的兵棋推演，歸納出「中共攻台七部曲」，認為台灣登陸戰將是歷史上最難的登陸戰，最終演變成長久消耗戰，不會數日內失陷。黃東更特別強調：「一旦大陸武統台灣，直接或間接參與國家可能不下於八國聯軍！」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201009/5YNCESLE6BCCFBLWILARXREMBI/?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post&amp;fbclid=IwAR1Jxe-kzozv265Vsp6i163gPhE_MniA-qsvkehk1R57EZlWd4F7x7hp-i4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201009%2F5YNCESLE6BCCFBLWILARXREMBI%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post%26fbclid%3DIwAR1Jxe-kzozv265Vsp6i163gPhE_MniA-qsvkehk1R57EZlWd4F7x7hp-i4&d=6zgGjWaceJ4ICz2LU8gYzugMmE0tIaoAQI%2BAeX1JER4%3D&h=dc183184\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201009%2F5YNCESLE6BCCFBLWILARXREMBI%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post%26fbclid%3DIwAR1Jxe-kzozv265Vsp6i163gPhE_MniA-qsvkehk1R57EZlWd4F7x7hp-i4&h=f9ce49e8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201009/5YNCESLE6BCCFBLWILARXREMBI/?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post&amp;fbclid=IwAR1Jxe-kzozv265Vsp6i163gPhE_MniA-qsvkehk1R57EZlWd4F7x7hp-i4</a>"},{"pid":"1a1dc58d2a11592f4a0907021c756c3a6dba0f33","tid":2236002,"uid":32675,"like":8